{"tid":1534112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際重要戰線] 光復香港足球 體育時代革命","createTime":"2019-09-03T01:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T14:41:05.000Z","uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"104059394768433fb8b035f0e188e354c9f69035","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:57:58.000Z","msg":"唔知大家仲記唔記得以下呢個畫面呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B-Uabv2JDWY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB-Uabv2JDWY&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=05994d16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B-Uabv2JDWY</a><br />\n好快香港隊又要打世界杯外圍賽啦<br />\n唔知大家又會唔會勁噓國歌呢？ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>法律分析</strong></span><br />\n雖然中國已經立咗國歌法，亦納入香港基本法附件三內<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港本地立法程序未完成</strong></span><br />\n同逃反條例一樣，國歌法都係停咗喺二讀階段未過哂<br />\n所以喺香港噓國歌今日<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仍然係未可以拉得</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">現時建議亦未有追溯條文</span></strong><br />\n如果有巴打喺球場噓國歌，應該到時仲未係觸犯香港法例<br />\n不過，如果到時立咗法大家就唔好做啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一有可能犯嘅係國際足協規例，亞洲足協上屆已經表明唔關佢事<br />\n同埋當時國際足協並不想介入言論自由上，係香港足總自己寫信罰自己<br />\n搞到足總先唔講貫切<strong>攬炒精神</strong>，其實仲<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔會有違政治倫理</span></strong>&hellip;&hellip;<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（睇下一節）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>道德分析</strong></span><br />\n香港隊雖然代表每一位香港市民，<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港足總由70年代起已經染紅</strong></span><br />\n當時中共亦由霍英東等代理人由令香港足球沒落原因<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">時至今日，足總仍然由土共把持，現任主席貝鈞奇更加之係六七暴動有份落場嘅恐怖土共</span></strong><br />\n如果支持香港而唔小心搞到香港足總，其實無所謂<br />\n因為<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港足總唔係中共代理人都係土共黎</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊登申延閱讀：<br />\n1) 香港足球的沒落原因: 中國共產黨<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5902704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5902704&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=927b0688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5902704</a><br />\n<br />\n有人或者問噓國歌呢種不合作運動會唔會帶黎反效果<br />\n咁請睇睇以下幾個例子：<br />\n1) 蘇格蘭噓足英國國歌幾十年<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=glLkwisH-ds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DglLkwisH-ds&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=8e4e473b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=glLkwisH-ds</a><br />\n2) 亞洲噓人地國歌第一代表：中國人噓日本國歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Zyd63DM4ZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4Zyd63DM4ZM&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=51a74e98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Zyd63DM4ZM</a><br />\n其實冇咩道德問題，最主要都係政治表態<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五大訴求做足哂唔噓又點話</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>賽程分析</strong></span><br />\n最重要係賽程，只有一場主場喺國慶前舉行<br />\n呢場賽事係對<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">9月10日對伊朗</span></span></strong><br />\n如果可以有大批球迷入場參與一定可以振奮大眾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScTd9uw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScTd9uw.jpg&h=eadadf26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzHOdWd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzHOdWd.png&h=35d66828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後一定要全心支持香港隊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時已經諗咗後續事項<br />\n不過想等大家討論一下先<br />\n有錯指正，有意見請提出<br />\n無嘢講請留句我無嘢講"},{"pid":"50706250a7e2dc05a75aa827c79e5583eedabdaa","tid":1534112,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:04:37.000Z","msg":"主線認真post又冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e427a8f89958747b2bd48c30d5e2869102905c","tid":1534112,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:05:13.000Z","msg":"其實長文都可以睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339baf8d0e7647db02b94faeb1fefb32ef55f7b2","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20e427a8f89958747b2bd48c30d5e2869102905c","tid":1534112,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:05:13.000Z","msg":"其實長文都可以睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"幫推10式？"},{"pid":"54f1f7d0e75f6db67164df960b2d4b16025c46ee","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:06:09.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"be069c731e7ef183bc50c4706f40f1e01bcaa193","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:06:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3053f68ea3c51e6166d6a9f14c58fc168550713","tid":1534112,"uid":19743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"782378c9936a1d426fbb25d712777fc64197e2ea","tid":1534112,"uid":19743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iDKtefj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiDKtefj.jpg&h=5c97866a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zey9H8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzey9H8E.jpg&h=ed0793a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cda6f8548575f82cc1f755cba0ecc4642ad9221","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d339a2d11dc0a8f1d6c971237c863ba0462a1132","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"c3668b6bb982a77445e35c598eb9a20d4a42beaf","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"125e2ecac4096e7ec3c5cd9ea89f42e9c2d6c399","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講？"},{"pid":"b94f1d6fc20d866b077d96859b6c05de24ada93d","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"毋忘721 831"},{"pid":"c03dad42762983c9d8c23b238d3f2e48e909e2e0","tid":1534112,"uid":120575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"想買件波衫支持港隊<br />\n但一諗起比錢香港個垃撚圾足總 就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f762645c49e4ff299f2a3e479734d8162f0a84f7","tid":1534112,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c03dad42762983c9d8c23b238d3f2e48e909e2e0","tid":1534112,"uid":120575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"想買件波衫支持港隊<br />\n但一諗起比錢香港個垃撚圾足總 就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"所以紅tee最好"},{"pid":"e9d5171721c2f496cbd0d3e9b04aa2dd67543e7d","tid":1534112,"uid":267843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"d96fca211ac85684700a5a7fa1b3a73f0c606b0a","tid":1534112,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3278e477cf407923291feb6f3ebe22ecb7a71525","tid":153411